---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Guides"
description: "Practical guides to modern job evaluation — methodology, checklists, governance, and ready-to-adapt templates from the Engage team."
permalink: /guides/
---
<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a><span>/</span>Guides</div>
    <div class="eyebrow">Practical insights</div>
    <h1>Guides for modern <em>job evaluation.</em></h1>
    <p class="lead">Field-tested guidance from the Engage team — the methodology explained, readiness checklists, governance discipline, and templates you can adapt for your own organisation.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="cases-section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="insights-grid">
      {%- for g in collections.guide %}
      <a class="insight-card guide-card" href="{{ g.url }}">
        <div class="insight-tag">{{ g.data.category }}{% if g.data.gated %} &middot; Gated{% endif %}</div>
        <h4>{{ g.data.title }}</h4>
        <p>{{ g.data.summary }}</p>
        <div class="guide-card-foot">
          <span>{{ g.data.readtime }}</span>
          {% if g.data.gated %}<span class="guide-lock">Email required</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="demo-cta" style="background:#005a7a;">
  <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="color:white;">Prefer to see it live?</h2>
    <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);max-width:560px;margin:14px auto 28px;">Book a working session and we&rsquo;ll grade a handful of your real roles using the Engage methodology.</p>
    <a class="btn-primary" href="/book-demo/">Book a demo</a>
  </div>
</section>
